tafsir[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,203,"Jaﾅ逆oree Innde Alla nden kabbirugol e haylilugol nder ﾉ殿lﾉ容 seeﾉ預aje, ﾉ容n ngoni: sappo e go'o, ﾉ擁ﾉ擁 e sappo e tati tafaske. On mo yaccini o yati Mina ﾉ殿awo bugagol kaaﾆｴe ﾉ容n ka sappo e ﾉ擁ﾉ預ﾉ兎re, no newii, kadi o alaa bakkaatu; tawde Alla no Hoynani mo ﾉ蓉m. On mo neﾉ鍍ini kadi haa ka sappo e tataﾉ兎re, no wenii, on kadi alaa bakkaatu; tawde o waﾉ擁i ko haani, o ﾃｱemtinii Annabiijo on mo jam e kisiyee woni e mun on. ﾆ隔m ﾉ熔o fof ko wanande on gomﾉ蓉ﾉ熔 ka hajju makko o gerdiri no Alla Yamiriri. Huliree Alla ﾃｱemitiﾅ吉ol Yamirooje Makko woﾉ遼擁too Haﾉ預aﾉ擁 Makko. Pelliton wonde onon ko ka Makko Kaﾅ橘o tan woni ko ruttete ﾉ熔n, ngam O Yoﾉ妬ta on golleeji mo'on."
  2,204,"Ko an Annbiijo, anndu no e yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n nafoqinﾉ熔 konngugol mun ka aduna ﾉ熔o, yi'iraa-mo moﾆｴﾆｴo-konngol, sikkiraa ﾉ蓉m ko o goongiyaﾅ橘e. Anndu non faandaare makko ko daﾉ溶dugol hoore-makko e jawdi makko. Hara non himo seediﾅ逆ina Alla (e hoore fenaande), kon ko woni e ﾉ兎rnde makko immorde e gomﾉ擁nal maa moﾆｴﾆｴere, e hoore non ko o saﾉ葉uﾉ熔 wennje e ngayngu juulﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  2,205,"Si o huccii ma o seedii e ma'a, o yaccora ka leydi fii bonnirgol gejji, e bonnital gese, e warugol neemoraaﾉ擁. Alla Yiﾉ預a bonnere ka leydi, O Yiﾉ預a kadi ﾉ兎n bonnooﾉ兎."
  2,206,"Si on bonnoowo wi'anaama (nde mo wasiyee): "Hulu Alla reﾅ逆oﾉ預a e Keeri Makko ﾉ擁n" mawnitaare nden haﾉ預 mo artugol e goonga kan, o heddoo e bakkaatu on. Njoﾉ電i makko ndin yonii naatugol jahannama, nge bonii ﾃｱiiﾉ妬rde sumooﾉ兎 nge."
  2,207,"No e yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n: gomﾉ擁nﾉ熔 sooﾉ葉iroowo woﾅ橘ii mun dewal Joomi makko, o tiiﾉ溶oo ﾉ預ﾉ橡兎re yaluyee Makko. Alla non ko Yaajuﾉ熔 yurmeede jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n, Hilnotooﾉ熔 ﾉ兎."
  2,208,"Ko onon yo gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 Alla e Nulaaﾉ熔 Makko on, naatiree e lislaamu mooﾉ堵al (denndanngal), wata on accu huunde e makko; wano yimﾉ兎 defte gerdata: ﾉ兎 gomﾉ擁na yoga ﾉ兎 yedda yoga. Wata on jokku ﾉ預te seytaane, on ko gaﾃｱo mooﾉ熔n ﾉ殿ﾅ杵gu ﾉ熔 ngyangu."
  2,209,"Si on arii ooﾃｱaade e muurtude ﾉ殿awo kon ko ari on e ﾉ殿ﾅ杵gannduyeeji feeﾃｱuﾉ擁, nganndee pellet, Alla ko Fooluﾉ熔 e Qudra Mu'un, ﾃ粗eﾃｱuﾉ熔 e Yiilugol Shari'aaji Makko. ﾆ隔m non, hulee Mo mawninon Mo."
  2,210,"ﾆ‘e jokkuﾉ兎 ﾉ預te seytaane murtuﾉ兎 e laawol goonga,ﾉ兎 sabbitaaki si wanaa nde Allaahu Seniiﾉ熔 On Ardaﾅ逆aﾉ兎 ﾃｱalnde darngal,e ndeer niﾉ兎 duule,fii no O ﾃ疎awira hakkunde maﾉ橡兎. Malaa'ika en kadi ngara ko ﾉ兎 kuuﾉ妬tuﾉ兎 ﾉ殿ﾅ杵ge fof, ontuma non fiyaake Alla on gasinee e maﾉ橡兎. Ko faade ka Alla Seniiﾉ熔 Bajjo On,woni ruttorde fiyakuuji tageefo ngon."